    <item>
      <title>鸡蛋短缺问题正在席卷餐馆，且看不到缓解的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/egg-shortages-spark-price-spikes-and-are-now-hitting-restaurants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国餐馆正成为全国性鸡蛋短缺的受害者，这种短缺已经困扰了从纽约到旧金山的杂货店，导致每箱鸡蛋价格上涨至 7 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/egg-shortages-spark-price-spikes-and-are-now-hitting-restaurants</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
